Introduction

Kim Jiwon, known under the stage name Liz, is a South Korean singer-songwriter and dancer under Starship Entertainment. She is best known as the main vocalist of the girl group IVE.

On November 12, 2021, Liz was revealed as the second member of IVE. The group officially debuted on December 1, 2021, with their single album "ELEVEN".

On November 10, 2023, Starship Entertainment confirmed Liz to be part of the special collaboration single "Nobody" with (G)I-DLE's Soyeon and aespa's Winter.The single was released on November 16, 2023.
